# onlineornot_browser_check (Resource)

Use `onlineornot_browser_check` to monitor a browser-rendered page or scripted Playwright flow.

This resource uses the typed `/v1/checks/browser` API. Browser checks are separate from uptime checks in Terraform even though some fields are shared.

## Example Usage

{{ tffile "examples/resources/onlineornot_browser_check/resource.tf" }}

## Notes

- Provide `url` for a simple page-load browser check.
- Provide `script` for a scripted Playwright check.
- `type` is managed by the provider and is always `BROWSER_CHECK` for this resource.
- Importing a non-browser monitor ID fails because reads go through the typed browser endpoint.

